Ab aapne job create kar li hai, toh Jenkins dashboard par jaakar "Build Now" dabayein.

Check karein ki Stage View mein "Checkout", "Build", aur "Test" green ho rahe hain ya nahi.

Check karein ki Console Output mein "SUCCESS" dikh raha hai.